                    <p class="card-text">A thrilling time-based challenge that requires players to master the game's map and achieve maximum efficiency within a limited timeframe.</p>
                    <p class="card-text">The creation of Time Slice exemplifies the enjoyment derived from the development process, mirroring the pleasure found in gameplay itself.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
